1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper focuses on generating textual descriptions of images, which is a problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper also involves natural language processing, as it generates descriptions in natural language. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The model used in the paper is a purely bilinear model, which is a type of machine learning model. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the use of AI techniques to generate descriptions of images. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves retrieving relevant information (descriptions) based on a given image sample.
